-- WorleyParsons Wins Contract for Queensland Curtis Liquified Gas Project
-- B y   V i c t o r i a   B a t c h e l o r
-- 2010-11-01T23:13:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-01/worleyparsons-wins-contract-for-queensland-curtis-liquified-gas-project.html
WorleyParsons Ltd. has been appointed
as the detailed engineering and procurement services contractor
for the upstream gas field facilities and related infrastructure
associated with Queensland Curtis LNG project. The potential
revenue from this contract is more than A$580 million, the
company said in a statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Victoria Batchelor at 
 vbatchelor@bloomberg.net  